title: Chanel Large Label Click Flap Bag
description: Chanel large Label Click flap bag in Khaki diamond-quilted calfskin leather (#23xxxxxx: 2016-2017). Featuring light gold-toned hardware, single leather handle, and chain shoulder strap with a leather shoulder pad. The push-lock closure with logo plate opens to a beige textile interior with a zipper pocket. Approximate dimensions: 29cm(L) x 19.5cm(H) x 8.5cm(D), handle drop 7.5cm, strap drop 51cm. With Entrupy Certificate of Authenticity. (Pre-owned)
